      <title>索马里地区计划对伊斯兰国发动新攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/oil-rich-somali-region-plans-new-offensive-against-islamic-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[半自治区邦特兰正计划发动新一轮攻势，打击索马里北部山区日益壮大的伊斯兰国叛乱势力。]]></description>
